Class Chunk

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.craft.world.Chunk
All Implemented Interfaces:
ServerDisposable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BuilderChunk, ClientChunk, ServerChunk
@NotThreadSafe @NonExtendable public abstract class Chunk extends Object implements ServerDisposable
Represents a chunk in the world.

NOTE: This class isn't meant to be extended

NOTE: This class isn't thread safe
